government%20that%20saw%20the%20country%20weather%20one%20of%20the%20more%20turbulent%20periods%20in%20its%20post-World%20War%20Two%20political%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20some%20of%20the%20defining%20moments%20of%20the%20Conservatives'%20four%20terms%20in%20power%20-%20under%20five%20prime%20ministers%20-%20since%202010%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E2010%20ELECTION%20RESULTS%20IN%20HUNG%20PARLIAMENT%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Conservative%20Party%20led%20by%20David%20Cameron%20wins%20the%20most%20seats%20in%20parliament%20but%20not%20an%20overall%20majority%2C%20ousting%20the%20Labour%20Party%20which%20had%20been%20in%20power%20since%201997.%20Britain%20has%20its%20first%20coalition%20government%20since%201945%2C%20after%20Cameron%20agrees%20to%20work%20with%20the%20centrist%20Liberal%20Democrats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E2014%20SCOTTISH%20REFERENDUM%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20referendum%20that%20had%20threatened%20to%20split%20the%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20Scotland%20votes%2055%25-45%25%20against%20independence%20in%20a%20victory%20for%20Cameron%20and%20the%20main%20national%20political%20parties%20over%20the%20Scottish%20National%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E2015%20SURPRISE%20CONSERVATIVE%20ELECTION%20VICTORY%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20polls%20pointing%20to%20a%20close%20election%2C%20Cameron%20wins%20an%20unexpected%20majority%20and%20a%20second%20term%20as%20prime%20minister.%20He%20follows%20through%20on%20a%202013%20pledge%20to%20hold%20a%20referendum%20on%20leaving%20the%20European%20Union.%20Cameron%20wants%20Britain%20to%20remain%20in%20the%20EU.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E2016%3A%20UK%20VOTES%20FOR%20BREXIT%2C%20CAMERON%20QUITS%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBritons%20cause%20a%20global%20shock%20by%20voting%2052%25-48%25%20to%20leave%20the%20EU%2C%20ending%20a%20more%20than%2040-year%20union%20and%20plunging%20the%20country%20into%20its%20biggest%20political%20crisis%20since%20World%20War%20Two.%20Cameron%20resigns%20and%20the%20party%20chooses%20Theresa%20May%20to%20succeed%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E2017%20SNAP%20ELECTION%20GAMBLE%20BACKFIRES%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERiding%20high%20in%20opinion%20polls%20and%20seeking%20a%20bigger%20majority%20in%20parliament%20to%20push%20Brexit%20legislation%20through%2C%20May%20calls%20a%20snap%20election.%20The%20Conservatives%20lose%20their%20majority%20and%20form%20a%20government%20by%20striking%20a%20deal%20with%20Northern%20Ireland's%20pro-UK%20Democratic%20Unionist%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EMAY%202019%3A%20BREXIT%20PARALYSIS%2C%20MAY%20RESIGNS%2C%20JOHNSON%20TAKES%20OVER%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMay%20quits%20after%20failing%20to%20break%20a%20parliamentary%20deadlock%20over%20how%20Britain%20should%20leave%20the%20EU.%20Boris%20Johnson%20-%20one%20of%20the%20main%20faces%20of%20the%20pro-Brexit%20campaign%20-%20wins%20the%20internal%20Conservative%20Party%20contest%20to%20succeed%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EDEC%202019%3A%20JOHNSON%20LEADS%20CONSERVATIVES%20TO%20SWEEPING%20WIN%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20parliament%20paralysed%20over%20Brexit%2C%20Johnson%20calls%20a%20snap%20election.%20Campaigning%20under%20the%20slogan%20%26quot%3BGet%20Brexit%20Done%26quot%3B%20he%20steers%20the%20Conservatives%20to%20their%20biggest%20election%20win%20since%20Margaret%20Thatcher's%20landslide%20victory%20in%201987.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E2020%20BREXIT%20GETS%20DONE%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJohnson%20used%20his%20mandate%20to%20drive%20a%20Brexit%20deal%20through%20parliament%20and%20Brussels%2C%20and%20Britain%20exited%20the%20EU%20on%20Jan.%2031%2C%202020%2C%20becoming%20the%20first%20state%20to%20withdraw%20from%20the%20bloc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EJULY%202022%3A%20JOHNSON%20OUSTED%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJohnson%20leads%20Britain%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pan