rtunate%20I%20am%20that%20I%20could%20afford%20it%20and%20about%20all%20those%20who%20cannot.%20And%20for%20the%20longest%20time%2C%20conventional%20treatments%20weren't%20making%20me%20better.%20There's%20a%20good%20chance%20it%20was%20just%20me%20and%20am%20sure%20they%20will%20work%20very%20well%20for%20others.%20These%20two%20factors%20led%20me%20to%20also%20read%20up%20on%20alternate%20therapies%20and%20treatments.%20And%20after%20trial%20and%20error%2C%20I%20found%20treatments%20that%20worked%20wonderfully%20for%20me.%20Treatments%20that%20also%20cost%20a%20fraction%20of%20what%20I%20was%20spending%20on%20conventional%20healthcare.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fsamantha-ruth-prabhus-big-birthday-announcement-new-project-bangaram-loading-5542177%5C%22%3ESamantha%20%3C%2Fa%3Esaid%20that%20she%20is%20%26quot%3Bnot%20naive%20enough%20to%20go%20about%20strongly%20advocating%20a%20treatment.%26quot%3B%20She%20maintained%20that%20she%20merely%20%26quot%3Bsuggested%20it%20with%20good%20intention%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20a%20%26quot%3Bhighly%20qualified%20doctor%26quot%3B%20suggested%20the%20treatment%20to%20her.%20An%20excerpt%20from%20her%20post%20read%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20merely%20suggested%20with%20good%20intention%20because%20of%20all%20that%20I%20have%20faced%20and%20learnt%20in%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years.%20Especially%20that%20treatments%20can%20be%20financially%20draining%20and%20many%20may%20not%20be%20able%20to%20afford%20them.%20End%20of%20the%20day%2C%20we%20all%20depend%20on%20educated%20doctors%20to%20guide%20us.%20This%20treatment%20was%20suggested%20to%20me%20by%20a%20highly%20qualified%20doctor%20who%20is%20an%20MD%2C%20who%20has%20served%20DRDO%20for%2025%20years.%20He%2C%20after%20all%20his%20education%20in%20conventional%20medicine%2C%20chose%20to%20advocate%20an%20alternate%20therapy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithout%20naming%20the%20doctor%20in%20her%20statement%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fsamantha-ruth-prabhu-and-warrior-hina-khans-instagram-exchange-takes-one-to-know-one-6016585%5C%22%3ESamantha%20Ruth%20Prabhu%3C%2Fa%3E%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20certain%20gentleman%20has%20attacked%20my%20post%20and%20my%20intentions%20with%20rather%20strong%20words.%20Said%20gentleman%20is%20a%20Doctor%20too.%20I%20have%20no%20doubt%20that%20he%20knows%20more%20than%20I%20do.%20And%20I%20am%20quite%20sure%20his%20intentions%20were%20noble.%20It%20would%20have%20been%20kind%20and%20compassionate%20of%20him%20had%20he%20not%20been%20so%20provocative%20with%20his%20words.%20Especially%20the%20bit%20where%20he%20suggests%20I%20should%20be%20thrown%20in%20prison.%20Never%20mind.%20I%20suppose%20it%20goes%20with%20the%20territory%20of%20being%20a%20celebrity.%20I%20posted%20as%20someone%20who%20needs%20medical%20treatments%20and%20not%20as%20a%20celebrity.%20And%20I%20certainly%20am%20not%20making%20any%20money%20from%20the%20post%20nor%20endorsing%20anyone.%20I%20was%20merely%20suggesting%20a%20treatment%20as%20an%20option%20after%20undergoing%20it%20myself%2C%20for%20others%20who%20may%20be%20looking%20for%20options%20because%20conventional%20medicine%20isn't%20working%20for%20them.%20Especially%20more%20affordable%20options.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Ftheliverdr%2Fstatus%2F1808804909783159003%5C%22%3EX%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%20recently%2C%20'The%20Liver%20Doc%2C'%20referring%20to%20Samantha's%20post%20about%20alternate%20treatments%2C%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BInfluential%20Indian%20actress%20Ms.%20Samantha%20Ruth%20who%20is%20unfortunately%20a%20health%20and%20science%20illiterate%20advising%20millions%20of%20her%20followers%20to%20inhale%20hydrogen-peroxide%20to%20prevent%20and%20treat%20respiratory%20viral%20infections.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actress%20added%20that%20it%20would%20have%20been%20nice%20if%20the%20%26quot%3Bsaid%20gentleman%20Doctor