to%20the%20Ganga%20was%20that%20I%20would%20give%20up%20shopping%20for%20this%20lifetime.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Murty%2C%2073%2C%20said%20in%20the%20interview%20that%20her%20commitment%20to%20this%20promise%20is%20deeply%20rooted%20in%20her%20upbringing%20as%20her%20parents%20and%20grandparents%20lived%20frugal%20lives%20with%20minimal%20possessions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20my%20mother%20passed%20away%20six%20years%20ago%2C%20it%20took%20us%20just%20half%20an%20hour%20to%20give%20away%20the%20things%20in%20her%20cupboard%20because%20she%20had%20just%208-10%20sarees%20in%20it.%20When%20my%20grandma%20passed%20away%2032%20years%20ago%2C%20she%20had%20just%20four%20sarees.%20They%20travelled%20light%20on%20this%20earth%2C%20and%20since%20that%20has%20been%20part%20of%20my%20upbringing%2C%20I%20found%20it%20easier%20to%20adopt%20a%20simpler%20life%20with%20fewer%20possessions%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20over%20two%20decades%2C%20Ms%20Murty%20has%20been%20wearing%20sarees%20gifted%20to%20her%20by%20her%20sisters%2C%20close%20friends%2C%20and%20occasionally%2C%20the%20NGOs%20she%20works%20with.%20Among%20her%20most%20cherished%20possessions%2C%20she%20said%2C%20are%20two%20hand-embroidered%20sarees%20given%20to%20her%20by%20a%20group%20of%20women%20whose%20lives%20she%20helped%20transform%20through%20her%20work%20with%20the%20Infosys%20Foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20her%20sisters%20initially%20gifted%20her%20a%20couple%20of%20sarees%20each%20year%2C%20Ms%20Murty%20eventually%20found%20the%20growing%20collection%20cumbersome%20to%20handle.%20%26quot%3BI%20told%20them%20enough%20of%20this%20gifting.%20I%20have%20too%20much%20already%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20been%20wearing%20sarees%20for%20fifty%20years%20now%20and%20I%20always%20make%20sure%20that%20I%20air%20them%20out%20after%20wearing%2C%20iron%20them%2C%20and%20keep%20them%20away.%20I%20don't%20wear%20my%20sarees%20so%20low%20that%20they%20sweep%20the%20floor%2C%20so%20they%20don't%20get%20dirty%20and%20have%20longer%20lives%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Infosys%20Foundation%20chairman%2C%20in%20her%20maiden%20speech%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20earlier%20this%20week%2C%20pitched%20for%20a%20government-sponsored%20vaccination%20program%20to%20combat%20cervical%20cancer.%20Ms%20Murty%20also%20called%20for%20the%20recognition%20of%2057%20domestic%20tourist%20sites%20as%20World%20Heritage%20Sites.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Murty%2C%20author%20of%20several%20books%2C%20mostly%20for%20children%2C%20was%20nominated%20to%20Rajya%20Sabha%20on%20International%20Women's%20Day%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720162320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F5c3kpos8_sudha-murty_625x300_27_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsudha-murty-reveals-why-she-hasnt-bought-a-saree-in-30-years-6038531%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20and%20engineer-turned-philanthropist%20Sudha%20Murty%20has%20revealed%20that%20she%20has%20not%20bought%20a%20saree%20in%2030%20years.%20The%20reason%3A%20a%20trip%20to%20Kashi.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsudha-murty-reveals-why-she-hasnt-bought-a-saree-in-30-years-6038531%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsudha-murty-reveals-why-she-hasnt-bought-a-saree-in-30-years-6038531%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsudha-murty-reveals-why-she-hasnt-bought-a-saree-in-30-years-6038531%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20top%20Russian%20banker%20says%20Russia's%20payment%20methods%20should%20be%20a%20'state%20secret'%20because%20the%20West%20keeps%20shutting%20them%20down%20so%20fast%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3