C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20according%20to%20a%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheins.press%2Fen%2Fpolitics%2F272870%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20The%20Insider%20and%20the%20German%20newspaper%20Der%20Spiegel.%20The%20organizations'%20joint%20investigation%20revealed%20the%20contents%20of%20a%20document%20obtained%20in%20a%20leak%20of%20SVR%20communications%20%E2%80%94%20detailing%20the%20ins%20and%20outs%20of%20Project%20Kylo%2C%20a%202022%20strategic%20plan%20to%20spread%20misinformation%20about%20Ukraine%20in%20the%20West.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20one%20of%20the%20operations%20in%20Project%20Kylo%20would%20have%20cost%20the%20Russian%20spies%20around%20%243%20a%20month%20to%20manipulate%20one%20Western%20internet%20user.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20main%20pillar%20of%20this%20campaign%20involved%20faking%20protests%2C%20with%20no%20more%20than%20100%20people%20being%20paid%20around%20%24108%20each.%20The%20false%20protests%20were%20filmed%20for%20%26quot%3Bsubsequent%20media%20dissemination%2C%26quot%3B%20per%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20part%20of%20the%20SVR's%20intelligence%20operations%20involved%20generating%20fake%20German%20news%20sites%20that%20branded%20themselves%20as%20independent%20investigations%20agencies.%20The%20sites%20churned%20out%20articles%20harping%20on%20economic%20issues%20in%20Germany%2C%20like%20homelessness%2C%20while%20disseminating%20content%20under%20incendiary%20headlines%20like%20%26quot%3BHow%20Ukrainians%20are%20robbing%20Germany%20of%20economic%20prosperity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BWaging%20network%20wars%20in%20EU%20cyberspace%20based%20on%20the%20increasing%20demands%20of%20Ukrainian%20migrants%20and%20the%20new%20waves%20of%20irritation%20of%20the%20local%20population%20provoked%20by%20this%2C%20according%20to%20preliminary%20estimates%2C%20will%20have%20a%20very%20high%20efficiency%20both%20now%20and%20in%20the%20foreseeable%20f