efully%20looking%20at%20their%20photograph.%20My%20heart%20breaks%20for%20her%20family%20who%20would%20have%20been%20looking%20forward%20to%20seeing%20her%20after%20a%20long%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Kaur%20was%20studying%20in%20Melbourne%20and%20wanted%20to%20become%20a%20chef.%20Her%20body%20cannot%20leave%20Australia%20because%20she%20died%20from%20tuberculosis%2C%20forcing%20her%20parents%20to%20apply%20for%20visas%20so%20they%20can%20fly%20to%20the%20country%20and%20attend%20their%20daughter's%20funeral.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20family%20said%20Ms%20Kaur's%20health%20had%20been%20rapidly%20deteriorating%20over%20recent%20month%20and%20she%20had%20%26quot%3Bdifficulty%20talking%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bno%20energy%20to%20do%20anything%26quot%3B%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmetro.co.uk%2F2024%2F07%2F05%2Fwomans-heartbreaking-last-words-dying-flight-21165451%2F%5C%22%3Eas%20per%20%3Cem%3EMetro%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20in%20Australia%20started%20the%20contact%20tracing%20the%20following%20day%2C%20and%20anyone%20identified%20as%20a%20potential%20risk%20is%20being%20notified.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720161780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fl831esmo_manpreet-kaur_625x300_01_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fco-flier-recalls-meeting-indian-origin-woman-who-died-mid-flight-her-innocent-face-6038584%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Manpreet%20Kaur%20was%20studying%20in%20Melbourne%20and%20wanted%20to%20become%20a%20chef.%20Her%20body%20cannot%20leave%20Australia%20because%20she%20died%20from%20tuberculosis.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fco-flier-recalls-meeting-indian-origin-woman-who-died-mid-flight-her-innocent-face-6038584%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2F