l%20Gandhi%20for%20visiting%20Aligarh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20called%20to%20someone%20else%20house%20to%20meet%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%20He%20asked%20about%20our%20well-being.%20I%20thanked%20him%20for%20visiting%20us.%20He%20said%20that%20he'll%20help%20from%20his%20side%20and%20the%20government%20side.%20Although%2C%20he%20should%20have%20come%20to%20our%20house%20also%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Police%20conducted%20a%20search%20operation%20at%20Ram%20Kutir%20Charitable%20Trust%20in%20Mainpuri%20on%20Thursday%20for%20the%20self-styled%20godman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20FIR%20has%20been%20registered%20in%20the%20incident%2C%20naming%20organizers%20of%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeputy%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20(DSP)%2C%20Mainpuri%20Sunil%20Kumar%20said%20yesterday%20that%20'Bhole%20Baba%20was%20not%20found%20inside%20his%20ashram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuperintendent%20of%20Hathras%20City%2C%20Rahul%20Mithas%20also%20said%20that%20they%20did%20not%20find%20the%20preacher%20in%20the%20ashram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20visited%20the%20site%20of%20the%20tragedy%20and%20ordered%20a%20judicial%20probe%20into%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20three-member%20Judicial%20Inquiry%20Commission%20under%20the%20chairmanship%20of%20Justice%20(retd)%20Brijesh%20Kumar%20Srivastava%20has%20been%20constituted%20to%20ensure%20comprehensiveness%20of%20the%20subject%20matter%20and%20transparency%20in%20the%20inquiry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Judicial%20Commission%20will%20investigate%20the%20stampede%20incident%20over%20the%20next%20two%20months%20and%20submit%20its%20report%20to%20the%20State%20Government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20prima%20facie%20report%2C%20the%20stampede%20took%20place%20when%20devotees%20rushed%20to%20seek%20blessings%20and%20collect%20soil%20from%20around%20the%20preacher's%20feet%2C%20but%20were%20stopped%20from%20doing%20so%20by%20his%20security%20personnel.%20They%20then%20started%20pushing%20one%20another%20due%20to%20which%20several%20people%20fell%20down%20triggering%20chaos%20at%20the%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720155540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F1dtadj7g_rahul-gandhi-hathras_625x300_05_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-leaves-for-hathras-will-meet-stampede-victims-families-6036977%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hathras%20stampede%20incident%3A%20Leader%20of%20the%20opposition%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20left%20for%20Hathras.%20He%20will%20be%20meeting%20the%20families%20affected%20by%20the%20stampede%2C%20that%20claimed%20the%20lives%20of%20123%20people.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-leaves-for-hathras-will-meet-stampede-victims-families-6036977%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-leaves-for-hathras-will-meet-stampede-victims-families-6036977%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-leaves-for-hathras-will-meet-stampede-victims-families-6036977%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China-made%20military%20drones%20similar%20to%20the%20MQ-9%20Reaper%20were%20disguised%20as%20wind%20turbines%20in%20shipments%20to%20Libya%3A%20Italian%20officials%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Italian%20officials%20uncover%20military%20drone%20parts%20disguised%20as%20wind%20turbine%20components.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F