nted%20in%20coins%20and%20pegged%20to%20the%20US%20dollar%20at%20%241%20to%20100%20centavos.%20This%20makes%20Timor-Leste%20more%20expensive%20than%20many%20other%20countries%20in%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Bali%2C%20a%20plate%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebalisun.com%2Fworlds-most-decadent-and-expensive-nasi-goreng-on-bali-beach-club-menu%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIn%2520popular%2520tourist%2520hotspots%252C%2520the%2Cpriced%2520between%2520IDR%2520120%252D180%252C000.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enasi%20goreng%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20an%20Indonesian%20fried%20rice%20with%20satay%20%E2%80%94%20costs%20an%20average%20of%20between%20%243%20to%20%244.50.%20In%20Dili%2C%20I%20paid%20between%20%2410%20and%20%2415%20for%20a%20similar%20dish.%20In%20Bali%2C%20renting%20a%20scooter%20for%20a%20day%20can%20cost%20as%20little%20as%20%243.%20In%20Dili%2C%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timorleste.tl%2Fplan-your-trip%2Ftransport%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecosts%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20five%20times%20more%2C%20between%20%2425%20and%20%2435.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2265e24fa0-c946-4582-8ca7-33fc8e4b0ddf%5C%22%3E4.%20Not%20everyone%20speaks%20the%20same%20language.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223232%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20working%20in%20a%20fabric%20shop%20in%20Timor-Leste%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6684b1a81f0c1cd6d7310f3e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222424%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAt%20least%2016%20languages%20are%20spoken%20in%20Timor-Leste%2C%20including%20Tetum%2C%20the%20most%20widely%20spoken.%3Cp%3EMarielle%20Descalsota%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Portuguese%20and%20Tetum%20are%20the%20official%20languages%20of%20Timor-Leste%2C%20English%20and%20Indonesian%20are%20the%20working%20languages.%20However%2C%20only%2013.5%25%20of%20locals%20speak%20Portuguese%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2F2009-2017.state.gov%2Foutofdate%2Fbgn%2Ftimorleste%2F101181.htm%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAs%2520a%2520result%2520of%2520the%2Caccording%2520to%2520the%25202004%2520census.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20State%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20majority%20of%20locals%20I%20met%20in%20Dili%20spoke%20Tetum%20and%20Indonesian.%20Due%20to%20the%20high%20number%20of%20ethnic%20groups%20in%20Timor-Leste%2C%20there%20are%20at%20least%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fminorityrights.org%2Fcountry%2Ftimor-leste%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E16%20additional%20languages%3C%2Fa%3E%20between%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20grew%20up%20in%20Singapore%20and%20can%20speak%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsolo-woman-female-traveler-backpacking-safety-asia-indonesia-jakarta-guide-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndonesian%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20when%20locals%20didn't%20speak%20English%2C%20that%20was%20my%20fallback%20language.%20Although%20Fernando%2C%20my%20guide%2C%20told%20me%20tourists%20needed%20to%20be%20careful%20when%20conversing%20in%20Indonesian.%20He%20noted%20that%20some%20locals%20may%20get%20offended%2C%20considering%20the%20complicated%20history%20between%20these%20countries.%20I%20found%20that%20it%20was%20best%20to%20ask%20what%20language%20they%20prefer%20to%20speak%20when%20in%20doubt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2269939375-afec-423a-9147-692be9d7cb72%5C%22%3E5.%20Very%20few%20American%20chains%20operate%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223022%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20caf%C3%A9%20overlooking%20Dili%20in%20Timor-Leste%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6684b2c1268f62ba18a6fd5d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222267%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E9Milhas%20d'Paraiso%2C%20a%20caf%C3%A9%20and%20memorial%20in%20the%20mountains%20of%20Timor-Leste%2C%20offered%20stunning%20views%20of%20Dili.%3Cp%3EMarielle%20Descalsota%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOnly%20a%20handful%20of%20American%20food%20chains%20exist%20in%20Timor-Leste%2C%20mostly%20in%20Dili's%20city%20center.%20I%20spotted%20a%20Burger%20King%20and%20a%20Gloria%20Jean's%20Coffee%20outlet%20next%20to%20each%20other%20right%20outside%20the%20hotel%20where%20I%20was%20staying%20%E2%80%94%20McDonald's%20doesn't%20operate%20in%20Timor-Leste.%20As%20an%20adventurous%20eater%2C%20I%20had%20all%20my%20meals%20at%20locally-run%20eateries%20and%20caf%C3%A9s%2C%20where%20I%20had%20Indonesian%20and%20Timorese%20fare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20stores%20sell%20American%20brands%20like%20Head%20and%20Shoulders%20and%20Maybelline%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20toiletries%20and%20makeup.%20But%20no-name%20brands%20are%20more%20common%20and%20are%20sold%20for%20much%20cheaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2271b61b0f-aec7-4ade-af7a-19c88c2aa686%5C%22%3E6.%20The%20landscapes%20are%20some%20of%20the%20most%20pristine%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222422%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20view%20of%20a%20beach%20in%20northern%20Dili%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6684b3691aace5b3ada3f1a1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221816%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20enjoyed%20swimming%20at%20Cristo%20Rei%20Beach%20in%20northern%20Dili.%3Cp%3EMarielle%20Descalsota%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20found%20that%20Timor-Leste%20offered%20some%20of%20the%20most%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsri-lanka-train-coast-colombo-ticket-price-route-photos-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Escenic%20views%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spent%20most%20of%20my%20time%20at%20Cristo%20Rei%20Beach%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20overlooked%20by%20an%2088-foot-long%20statue%20of%20Jesus%20Christ%20%E2%80%94%20at%20the%20northern%20tip%20of%20Dili.%20It's%20a%20natural%20white-sand%20beach%20with%20the%20cle