_blank%5C%22%3Ecan%20be%20aggressive%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20part%20of%20the%20reason%20why%20science%20knew%20little%20about%20how%20hippos%20move%20before%20our%20research%2C%26quot%3B%20Hutchinson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpeerj.com%2Farticles%2F17675%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epublished%20their%20findings%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20peer-reviewed%20PeerJ%20journal.%20It%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20whether%20the%20footage%20of%20the%20airborne%20hippos%20becomes%20as%20iconic%20as%20Muybridge's%20horse%20photos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhippos-airborne-when-trot-run-video-footage-proof-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720137290000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66871d37268f62ba18a791d1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhippos-airborne-when-trot-run-video-footage-proof-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Researchers%20realized%20hippos%20become%20airborne%20when%20they%20trot.%20They%20made%20the%20discovery%20watching%20footage%20that%20showed%20hippos%20fully%20lifting%20off%20the%20ground.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jmcgrath%40insider.com%20(Jenny%20McGrath)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A495%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhippos-airborne-when-trot-run-video-footage-proof-2024-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98The%20Invasion%E2%80%99%20Review%3A%20Sergei%20Loznitsa%E2%80%99s%20Raw%20but%20Restrained%20Reflection%20on%20Life%20During%20Wartime%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720136345000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FThe-Invasion-2.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236060649%22%2C%22summa