arning%20more%20about%20this%20model%2C%20you%20can%20email%20them%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ameruaveksha%40meruinternationalschool.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Emeruaveksha%40meruinternationalschool.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20to%20prevent%20children%20being%20left%20alone%20at%20home.%20Every%20child%20deserves%20a%20good%20education%20and%20a%20chance%20at%20a%20better%20life.%20Let%E2%80%99s%20give%20them%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Meghana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720016654000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fmeru-daycare-1720005938.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D355387%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Meghana%20Gorukanti%20Jupally%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Meru%20International%20School%20has%20launched%20a%20daycare%20centre%20called%20Meru%20Aveksha%2C%20which%20helps%20integrate%20kids%20of%20migrant%20workers%20into%20mainstream%20education.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F355387%2Fmeru-international-school-tellapur-hyderabad-migrant-workers-children-daycare-learning-centre%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Google's%20greenhouse%20gas%20emissions%20have%20surged%2048%25%20in%20five%20years%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720013160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F07%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-google-data-center_6597538.jpg%3F20240703143405%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fai-why-googles-greenhouse-gas-emissions-have-surged-48-in-five-years-13162922%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Google%20has%20admitted%20its%20greenhouse%20gas%20emissions%20have%20r